Package ooga.model.initialization

Class BoardCreator

java.lang.Object
ooga.model.initialization.Creator
ooga.model.initialization.BoardCreator
public class BoardCreator
extends Creator
This class creates a 2D GamePiece array that represents the game board, adjustable by the starting state XML files which describe each occupied square in the board in addition to board dimensions
